{"tid":1849494,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"口罩短缺 何去何從?","createTime":"2020-01-29T05:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T03:36:15.000Z","uid":186531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef33baa9855e1fcef15e0e47eaecfbc3c487bce7","tid":1849494,"uid":186531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T05:47:32.000Z","msg":"呢幾日風向變得很快,我們知道有一班炒家存在,這幾天1月28,29日的香港市場，資訊不多,已經出現恐慌。我在這裡只是分享新聞觀察,我非專家,不能作準,同時亦無法給甚麼有力建議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1月7日新聞:<br />\n湖北武漢爆發不明病毒性肺炎，雖然仍然未有確診個案，但已經人心惶惶。不少藥房甚至「坐地起價」，但仍不乏市民問津。港九藥房總商會估計，半數藥房出現口罩供應短缺。<br />\n<br />\n在九龍灣，有職員表示近日外科口罩需求大增兩至三倍，供應商暫時亦未有貨提供。在荃灣，有市民傍晚放工去藥房，盒裝已經售罄，買了2包成人口罩，已經是店內最後存貨，只剩下兒童口罩。<br />\n<br />\n不少藥房就將口罩放在門口當眼位置，更炒高幾個價位，有兒童口罩售價被炒近4、5倍，成人口罩亦近乎1倍。有平日售50多元的50個裝的口罩，索價500元。雖然被炒高，仍有大批市民問津，大量藥房口罩幾乎全部售罄。<br />\n<br />\n來自 <a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1175623/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%92%B2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8B500%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92-%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%96%99%E5%8D%8A%E6%95%B8%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1175623%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2592%25B2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%25A6%258B500%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592-%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A8&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=0c28d175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1175623%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2592%25B2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%25A6%258B500%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592-%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%2597%25A5%25E6%2588%25BF%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E8%25B2%25A8&h=df6bb4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1175623/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E6%92%B2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8B500%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92-%E5%95%86%E6%9C%83%E6%96%99%E5%8D%8A%E6%95%B8%E8%97%A5%E6%88%BF%E7%BC%BA%E8%B2%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華昨日1月28日記者會上聲稱：「過去一個多星期以來，經兩地海關協調後，一些已訂購的物資得以運到香港，為數達數百萬。」(可靠?)<br />\n<br />\n來自 <a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/01/20200128/20200128_183149_913.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2020%2F01%2F20200128%2F20200128_183149_913.html&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=9383320b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2020/01/20200128/20200128_183149_913.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們現在無可靠數據，我嘗試參考網絡上03年SARS的數據:<br />\n台灣:「從5月份起每天都有約200萬個口罩大量進口」 <br />\n來自 <a href=\"https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/6367/BN-ARTICLE-6367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bnext.com.tw%2Farticle%2F6367%2FBN-ARTICLE-6367&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=deb4d4fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bnext.com.tw/article/6367/BN-ARTICLE-6367</a><br />\n<br />\n今日台灣:「目前，國內產能每天能夠生產188萬個口罩，最高產能還可以到達244萬個。平常國內需求是130萬個，其餘外銷。」<br />\n來自 <a href=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209688/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail%2F209688%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%25B6%2593%25E6%25BF%259F%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%2581%259C%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E5%2584%25AA%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%2587%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%25B1%2582&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=ae8060f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail/209688/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E9%83%A8%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-%E5%84%AA%E5%85%88%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82</a> <br />\n<br />\n(台灣人如果你現在見到,好好思考現在的情況,是否和2003年搶口罩有點類似?我們很需要你的經驗。要小心,我們都不希望再有其他地區出事)<br />\n<br />\n假若市場無法維持口罩供應,我們應該何去何從?<br />\n<br />\n減少出外次數?<br />\n加強資訊流通?(教育身邊家人多留意新聞,list out高危區域；加緊留意有甚麼藥房買賣假口罩)<br />\n加緊清潔?(清潔家中去水口。)<br />\n<br />\n六月以來,連登已經有極多五毛混淆視聽,我相信現在也有很多炒家散播恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n大家保重身體。"},{"pid":"b6e4d18d5d299814415dbd5329355fbf5d0dbc81","tid":1849494,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:36:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=26a2e161\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=1c3a4bd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7JiK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=e4ddfa6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底"}]}